replies.body:
Awesome leader, and remember it's never your fault if we lose a scrim. It's a team loss. We should really talk more +-+!

Definitely visit Calgary again, and possibly meet up with some of my online friends :c?

@ Jess

I'm so hooked on Zootopia right now HAHAHAHAAH

Twenty One Pilots :c. Or that new Grace girl on AGT, She's goals :3

Jess, you're basically my bestie! I love talking to you and snapchatting 24/7 haha. You're so nice to work with during the tournament and we should of really met up when we had the chance. Maybe some other time :(. But you are definitely one of my best friends here, we need to talk more!!

@ Blaze

Josh :)

I don't really know, just sounded pretty cool.

After my run of junior mod I still wanted to get involved and tried applying for referee. I liked the idea of watching live tournament matches looking for cheater, glitchers, hackers etc. It was also a great way to get involved with the competitive side of Avicus.

Probably from global warming.

1. Too have as much money as I want.
2. Be able to teleport wherever I want whenever.
3. To have 100 more wishes ;)

Super cool and I definitely think you'd be hopefully the next official ;P. I've never really heard you talk before though. :(

@ Borrah

Super awesome. I had a great talk with you yesterday and it was really fun playing (or defending should I say) with you. You should apply for junior mod, I think it would fit you very well. See you on Saturday!

@ ElementalAssasin

Kind of salty at some times but we've scrimmed together before and had some fun .
adventures.

If you try your hardest. Just don't get too salty over some stuff!

Yep, all the time.
